@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About — Brave Goose Skate Emporium</PageTitle>

<section class="about-page">
    <h1>About the Emporium</h1>
    <div class="about-content">
        <p class="about-lead">
            Founded on the radical notion that skaters deserve better than grungy basements
            and questionable bearing grease, <strong>Brave Goose Skate Emporium</strong> is
            the world's most distinguished purveyor of skateboarding equipment and apparel.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our crest — a noble goose in full knight's armour — represents the duality of our craft:
            the grace of a well-executed kickflip and the stubborn courage required to attempt it
            again after landing on your face.
        </p>
        <p>
            Every product in our collection is curated with the same care a headmaster gives to
            selecting the school blazer. We believe that dropping in on a vert ramp should feel
            as dignified as arriving at a black-tie gala — just with more knee pads.
        </p>
        <h2>Our Houses</h2>
        <div class="houses-grid">
            <div class="house-card house-knights">
                <h3>Knight's Choice</h3>
                <p>Our premium line. Decks and gear worthy of the round table.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="house-card house-colours">
                <h3>House Colours</h3>
                <p>Signature apparel bearing the Brave Goose crest.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="house-card house-quad">
                <h3>The Quad</h3>
                <p>Park-ready hardware for the courtyard sessions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="house-card house-crest">
                <h3>Crest Collection</h3>
                <p>Heritage pieces. Timeless. Unbreakable (mostly).</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
